milestones.description: Callender has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for CAN, going past Mauricette's 1
Chappell has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (3) for CAN, going past Dennis
Valentine has conceded the most runs in an innings (28) in ODIs for CAN, going past Patel's record of 27
John Vaughan and Tariq Javed's 27-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 8 between Dennis and Marshall
Patel and Henry's 6-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 1 between Mauricette and Henry
